{"tid":2515863,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"14歲男童把小龍蝦塞進肛門隨後送醫，男童辯稱「想讓牠變蝦乾」","createTime":"2021-05-04T09:20:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T09:42:50.000Z","uid":38539,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"97421f53b528caa7d2de271e523d72f2c7bbe33b","tid":2515863,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T09:20:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWKym3K3PRJmSNQ2x5HTU4YaVQcfs9h9he5q7bSfney5b?filename=bc9HOuB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbc9HOuB.jpg&h=d002a2d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據《都市快報》報導，4月25日，中國浙江省人民醫院肛腸外科主治醫師戴俏瓊收治一位14歲的男患者，因為男患者把小龍蝦塞進肛門了，「我看到手機上有一檔野外求生的節目，那個老外把海水灌進自己的肛門。我也學他的樣，想用肛門吸收小龍蝦的水分，把牠變成一隻龍蝦乾。」<br />\n<br />\n「只有做大腸鏡手術，把小龍蝦取出來」，最終在距離肛門10公分處，也就直腸中上端，一隻小龍蝦赫然出現在電腦上。尖利的蝦螯，已把小作的直腸內璧，蟄出一道道血絲。確定目標後，醫生一根長長的細鐵絲圈套器塞進肛門內，小龍蝦被圈套器的橢圓頂端套住，隨後輕輕一拉，小龍蝦就從掰開的屁股裡出來了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmccd2FBGFCJtdLAeu8XLR4pTSDKGRGCu4aQ4amjgY23Lk?filename=noajQH2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnoajQH2.png&h=b31e9fb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小龍蝦被取出後放在手術台的紗布上，此時已分成兩截，一動不動死了。據悉，這是中國首例從肛裡取出小龍蝦的手術。醫生提醒，千萬不要因為一時好奇心驅使，或者追求刺激，在肛門內塞任何東西，以免危害健康。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210504/WTTMYRP73ZATHDTMWZKZVIJ6B4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210504%2FWTTMYRP73ZATHDTMWZKZVIJ6B4%2F&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnpriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=bf6a8509\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210504%2FWTTMYRP73ZATHDTMWZKZVIJ6B4%2F&h=ef671efa\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210504/WTTMYRP73ZATHDTMWZKZVIJ6B4/</a>"},{"pid":"66d3f1bab5fbbb6319e053b6ea0a78d3fe91145d","tid":2515863,"uid":34666,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T09:21:13.000Z","msg":"肛棗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"210bf63e84cc532266bbea66cdf0279c22830536","tid":2515863,"uid":183758,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T09:22:39.000Z","msg":"究竟支那仔係咪智撚障<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcd694c8df915b37285ba37beac5469f65d8dc48","tid":2515863,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T09:24:08.000Z","msg":"零仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93e02184518581259803cf84979a277a8399c02c","tid":2515863,"uid":269864,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T09:24:19.000Z","msg":"蝦乾定蝦肛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef653e1b177cfa56a984f4b8f21eb60c113bf101","tid":2515863,"uid":302471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T09:25:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f34d1f4b73a8c47f289ca873e2a951887f214444","tid":2515863,"uid":88886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T09:26:24.000Z","msg":"死於非命<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"147ea6dc6ed9a4457bd633109444e62f8fd1210c","tid":2515863,"uid":5490,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T09:27:45.000Z","msg":"條友拎白卡？"},{"pid":"9b34ccfbbb63b0b708e4df9d81155157260cbe8c","tid":2515863,"uid":4811,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T09:29:54.000Z","msg":"佢哋特別鍾意呢種生物，buffet 攞親都係佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87fef8be6e11d0f3396c173d71f351d0f0626aa6","tid":2515863,"uid":29423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T09:31:30.000Z","msg":"Gerbilling <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"h